'''VRCat''' is the official mascot of [[Special:MyLanguage/VRChat|VRChat]], a spacefaring orange cat with white markings. He wears a box on his head, with the [[VRC+]] symbol on the side.

==Appearances ==
VRCat's first appearance was [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=z-MKanCkDck Introducing VRChat Plus] and has been seen in numerous official VRChat announcements and social media posts since.

VRCat appears as the Early Supporter [[Badges|Badge]] for users who bought [[VRC+]] when it was first released. The badge can be pet on a user's profile on the website.

