== VRCat avatars ==
VRCat has two [[avatars]], created by VRChat's team, and are part of the list of available [[Public Avatars|public avatars]].

=== VRCat ===
The first [https://vrchat.com/home/avatar/avtr_30451089-312d-4daf-b798-f57da776ad02 avatar] simply called '''VRCat''' was uploaded by ''Creator Support'' on April 4, 2024. This avatar is cross-compatible, and the description of this avatar reads: "Thank you for supporting VRChat!".

